text: Horáček (feminine Horáčková) is a Czech surname, it may refer to: * Barbora Horáčková, Czech archer * Jan Horáček, Czech professional ice hockey player * Judy Horacek (born 1961), Australian cartoonist, illustrator and writer * Michal Horáček (born 1952), Czech entrepreneur, producer * Michal Horáček (orienteer), Czech orienteering competitor * Mike Horacek (born 1973), American football wide receiver * Milan Horáček (born 1946), German politician, a founding member of the German Green Party, and a former MEP * Petr Horáček, Czech boxer * Tony Horacek (born 1967), retired Canadian professional ice hockey left winger == See also == * Horák Category:Czech- language surnames
title: Horáček
